Key Match Events: Patson Daka scored a late equalizer to secure a 1-1 draw for Zambia
Simon Msuva gave Tanzania the lead with an early goal
Tanzania's first group F win in the tournament was denied by the late equalizer
Pre-Game Insights: Tanzania was expected to struggle due to their poor previous performance and coach suspension
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match affected the group standings
Earlier DR Congo held Morocco to a draw
